{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2001_00_01","textHome":"虽然还有很多不明白的事情，但在麻美学姐的@教导下，我也想靠自己的努力，成为能帮上@大家的魔法少女……啊，光是想可不行！@我在努力！啊，对了！之前，麻美学姐还@夸奖了我呢！诶嘿嘿......"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"id":200100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp.json","id":200100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200100}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2001_00_18","textHome":"沙耶香和杏子也成为了朋友了哦。虽然她们两个@总是吵架，但关系很好呢！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp.json","id":200100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":100}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2001_00_19","textHome":"现在的我怎么样？有什么奇怪的地方吗……？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200100}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2001_00_20","textHome":"怎么回事呢……感觉眼前都变明亮了……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":200100,"motion":200}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":8.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2001_00_21","textHome":"我们家是妈妈在外工作，爸爸在家料理家务。@所以爸爸是家庭主夫。@不过，大家关系很好哦！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":100}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2001_00_22","textHome":"家人、朋友或是魔法少女同伴们，@大家都是我所珍视的人。@所以，有什么事我都要帮助他们。@如果这些都是魔女的罪行，@那我就得更加努力才行呢。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":200}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2001_00_23","textHome":"虽然只是假设……如果有一天遇到了很强的@魔女，我还能够战斗下去吗……但是，不管@对方多强，我也不会放弃保护大家的使命。@希望一定是存在的，对吧……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":100}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2001_00_24","textHome":"太好了！找到你了！其他人也在等着我们呢。@热闹一点更让人开心！走吧，一起去吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":100}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2001_00_25","textHome":"起床啦！早上好！天已经亮了哦~。我吗？@嗯，我睡得很香哦。所以现在精神百倍！@睡眠是很重要的哦~"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":0}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2001_00_26","textHome":"一起吃便当吧！今天有——煎鸡蛋、炸鸡块@还有蔬菜！……啊呜，好好吃~@啊，炸鸡块味道怎么样？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":200100,"motion":100}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2001_00_27","textHome":"今天和子老师也沉醉在自己爱人的话题中呢~@看样子这次持续了好久，@希望她能永远这么幸福。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":100}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2001_00_03","textHome":"为了不拖累麻美学姐，我要变得更强才行！"}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2001_00_28","textHome":"呀！要做明天的预习才行！@要是被点名就惨了……@但是，也有想看的节目……@就看那么一小会儿电视，应该没问题吧？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp.json","id":200100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp.json","id":200100}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2001_00_29","textHome":"成为魔法少女到现在，@虽然感觉只是转瞬之间，@却发生了很多的事呢~@真让人惊讶。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":0}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2001_00_30","textHome":"小焰转学来的第一天起，@我就和她相处得很好。@我们是彼此非常重要的朋友哦。@对吧，小焰？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":200100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp.json","id":200100}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2001_00_31","textHome":"虽然知道是冒牌货，但是和同样的魔法少女战斗@还是有点……嗯——啊，对了！就当是@和魔女战斗之前的练习不就行了嘛！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.3,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":300}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2001_00_32","textHome":"这里会有和我一样的新手吗……@啊——不行不行！没问题！我一定没问题的！@加油！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200100}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2001_00_33","textHome":"这条缎带怎么样？@妈妈说「女人因外表而被轻视的话就完了哦」，@就给我选了这条缎带……是不是有点花哨呢？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp.json","id":200100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":0}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2001_00_34","textHome":"抢答时间！荷包蛋是全熟好，还是半熟好？@老师说，答案是……「都行啦！」"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp.json","id":200100}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2001_00_35","textHome":"我长大后会变成什么样子呢……？@会变成妈妈那样工作麻利的人吗……@呜哇，完全没法想象……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200100}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2001_00_36","textHome":"我的朋友仁美收到了好多情书啊。@不过，上面到底写了些什么呢……@好想看看啊。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":100}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2001_00_37","textHome":"果然，真正和魔女战斗的时候还是有点害怕，@没办法平静下来……@不过，想到自己是为了什么人而战斗的时候，@就能提起干劲了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":0}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2001_00_04","textHome":"能做出这样的事的，只有魔女吧……!?"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200100}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2001_00_38","textHome":"我没有什么擅长的学科，@也没有什么值得骄傲的才能……@但是，如果我能成为像麻美学姐那样@对别人有用的人，我就满足了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200100}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2001_00_39","textHome":"上条的手治好之后，@沙耶香的心情变得好多了。@说总是情不自禁想要夸奖自己呢。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":200100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"c